[
    {
        "text": "- Okay.",
        "start": 0.4,
        "duration": 0.86
    },
    {
        "text": "Hey, everyone.",
        "start": 1.26,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Hope you're having an amazing day.",
        "start": 2.093,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "It's Mark Wiens.",
        "start": 2.926,
        "duration": 0.834
    },
    {
        "text": "We just arrived to Ang Thong,\nwhich is right in central...",
        "start": 3.76,
        "duration": 3.65
    },
    {
        "text": "Right in the heart of Thailand.",
        "start": 7.41,
        "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
        "text": "We're on our way today for lunch to eat at",
        "start": 9.01,
        "duration": 1.9
    },
    {
        "text": "a place called Pad Thai Ba Lek,",
        "start": 10.91,
        "duration": 2.31
    },
    {
        "text": "which is a lady.",
        "start": 13.22,
        "duration": 1.53
    },
    {
        "text": "She's 85 years old,",
        "start": 14.75,
        "duration": 2.06
    },
    {
        "text": "and she's been making pad\nthai for over 45 years.",
        "start": 16.81,
        "duration": 3.54
    },
    {
        "text": "So it's gonna be an honor.",
        "start": 20.35,
        "duration": 1.72
    },
    {
        "text": "We're gonna go to her restaurant.",
        "start": 22.07,
        "duration": 1.82
    },
    {
        "text": "We're gonna see her make pad thai.",
        "start": 23.89,
        "duration": 1.66
    },
    {
        "text": "Feels good to be in the\ncountrysides, the rice fields.",
        "start": 25.55,
        "duration": 3.26
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, we're on our way to go eat pad thai.",
        "start": 28.81,
        "duration": 2.456
    },
    {
        "text": "(emphatic, rhythmic music)",
        "start": 31.266,
        "duration": 3.583
    },
    {
        "text": "(rustling gravel)",
        "start": 38.01,
        "duration": 2.899
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh, man, the breeze under\nthis mango tree is wonderful.",
        "start": 40.909,
        "duration": 2.701
    },
    {
        "text": "And, yeah, it was about an hour and a half",
        "start": 43.61,
        "duration": 1.77
    },
    {
        "text": "drive from Central Bangkok.",
        "start": 45.38,
        "duration": 2.91
    },
    {
        "text": "We are in the province\nand I think pretty close",
        "start": 48.29,
        "duration": 2.57
    },
    {
        "text": "to the city of Ang Thong,",
        "start": 50.86,
        "duration": 2.23
    },
    {
        "text": "but we're in the countryside.",
        "start": 53.09,
        "duration": 1.7
    },
    {
        "text": "It's beautiful out here.",
        "start": 54.79,
        "duration": 1.65
    },
    {
        "text": "The breeze.",
        "start": 56.44,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "The rice fields are in\nfull green, yellow blossom.",
        "start": 57.44,
        "duration": 4.343
    },
    {
        "text": "Just a few kilometers down the road",
        "start": 63.429,
        "duration": 1.131
    },
    {
        "text": "should be the restaurant.",
        "start": 64.56,
        "duration": 0.976
    },
    {
        "text": "(door opens)\n(engine idling)",
        "start": 65.536,
        "duration": 3.444
    },
    {
        "text": "(door shuts)\n(airy, rhythmic music)",
        "start": 68.98,
        "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
        "text": "(lively rhythmic music)",
        "start": 75.228,
        "duration": 3.333
    },
    {
        "text": "(door shuts)",
        "start": 87.027,
        "duration": 0.913
    },
    {
        "text": "This is an amazing location\nnext to a canal of water.",
        "start": 87.94,
        "duration": 3.74
    },
    {
        "text": "There's a really old...",
        "start": 91.68,
        "duration": 1.53
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, there's a modern bridge\nthat you can drive across.",
        "start": 93.21,
        "duration": 1.85
    },
    {
        "text": "Then there's this ancient,\nold, rickety, wooden bridge.",
        "start": 95.06,
        "duration": 3.95
    },
    {
        "text": "It's so peaceful.",
        "start": 99.01,
        "duration": 1.64
    },
    {
        "text": "We got a parking right under\nthis beautiful shade tree,",
        "start": 100.65,
        "duration": 2.69
    },
    {
        "text": "and then the whole restaurant is",
        "start": 103.34,
        "duration": 1.04
    },
    {
        "text": "kind of under a shelter with tables.",
        "start": 104.38,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "I love this style of a restaurant.",
        "start": 106.48,
        "duration": 2.297
    },
    {
        "text": "(rattling)",
        "start": 108.777,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "(background conversations\nin foreign language)",
        "start": 109.61,
        "duration": 1.187
    },
    {
        "text": "(steaming and sizzling)",
        "start": 110.797,
        "duration": 3.333
    },
    {
        "text": "(metal scraping)",
        "start": 115.414,
        "duration": 2.75
    },
    {
        "text": "(taps)\n(metal scraping)",
        "start": 121.958,
        "duration": 2.922
    },
    {
        "text": "She's a legend.",
        "start": 124.88,
        "duration": 0.85
    },
    {
        "text": "She's over 85 years old, and\nshe's still making pad thai.",
        "start": 125.73,
        "duration": 3.51
    },
    {
        "text": "She's cooking at the\nback of the restaurant",
        "start": 129.24,
        "duration": 2.08
    },
    {
        "text": "burning only wood so\nyou get the wood smoke.",
        "start": 131.32,
        "duration": 2.81
    },
    {
        "text": "You can smell the aroma of\nthe fire, the combustion,",
        "start": 134.13,
        "duration": 3.17
    },
    {
        "text": "but I kinda came around to the back",
        "start": 137.3,
        "duration": 1.33
    },
    {
        "text": "so I could see her from the\nfront where she's cooking.",
        "start": 138.63,
        "duration": 2.89
    },
    {
        "text": "And she's right in the middle of a batch.",
        "start": 141.52,
        "duration": 2.59
    },
    {
        "text": "She makes it by a whole\nwok batch, all the noodles.",
        "start": 144.11,
        "duration": 2.95
    },
    {
        "text": "Just juices and sauces\nare just sloshing around.",
        "start": 147.06,
        "duration": 4.95
    },
    {
        "text": "Then she only uses duck eggs.",
        "start": 152.01,
        "duration": 1.46
    },
    {
        "text": "So then, when she's finishing a batch,",
        "start": 153.47,
        "duration": 1.72
    },
    {
        "text": "she adds on the duck eggs\nkind of into portions,",
        "start": 155.19,
        "duration": 1.463
    },
    {
        "text": "kind of like divvying out the portions.",
        "start": 156.653,
        "duration": 2.277
    },
    {
        "text": "Hopefully, we'll see the\nentire process from the start",
        "start": 158.93,
        "duration": 3.01
    },
    {
        "text": "after she finishes this batch.",
        "start": 161.94,
        "duration": 1.87
    },
    {
        "text": "But just the way she works like not fast,",
        "start": 163.81,
        "duration": 2.87
    },
    {
        "text": "just methodically, slowly dropping in",
        "start": 166.68,
        "duration": 3.24
    },
    {
        "text": "those duck eggs with one hand,",
        "start": 169.92,
        "duration": 2.63
    },
    {
        "text": "sloshing them around,\nstirring them around,",
        "start": 172.55,
        "duration": 2.38
    },
    {
        "text": "scrambling them into the pad\nthai noodle sloshy mixture.",
        "start": 174.93,
        "duration": 4.989
    },
    {
        "text": "(metallic clanging)\n(plastic ruffling)",
        "start": 179.919,
        "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
        "text": "The rice noodles are\nfirst soaked in water,",
        "start": 186.56,
        "duration": 2.73
    },
    {
        "text": "and then they're fried once.",
        "start": 189.29,
        "duration": 2.07
    },
    {
        "text": "It's dry chili?",
        "start": 191.36,
        "duration": 1.09
    },
    {
        "text": "Like dried chili, right?",
        "start": 192.45,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "She adds in dried chili as well as",
        "start": 193.283,
        "duration": 2.657
    },
    {
        "text": "hom dang, which are shallots.",
        "start": 195.94,
        "duration": 2.37
    },
    {
        "text": "And that just gives the\nnoodles their primer,",
        "start": 198.31,
        "duration": 3.233
    },
    {
        "text": "prepares them for the real fry,",
        "start": 202.82,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
        "text": "for the real slosh in all of the sauces.",
        "start": 204.5,
        "duration": 2.29
    },
    {
        "text": "And then they go into\nanother pan to be fried again",
        "start": 206.79,
        "duration": 3.74
    },
    {
        "text": "with the eggs, with more sauce, with lard",
        "start": 211.466,
        "duration": 2.074
    },
    {
        "text": "to give it the final flavor.",
        "start": 213.54,
        "duration": 1.54
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, she's about to\nstart a fresh, new batch.",
        "start": 215.08,
        "duration": 2.393
    },
    {
        "text": "(tapping)",
        "start": 221.157,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "(speaking in foreign language)",
        "start": 221.99,
        "duration": 1.595
    },
    {
        "text": "(sizzling oil)",
        "start": 223.585,
        "duration": 2.316
    },
    {
        "text": "(speaking in foreign language)",
        "start": 225.901,
        "duration": 1.66
    },
    {
        "text": "(sizzles)",
        "start": 227.561,
        "duration": 0.904
    },
    {
        "text": "(speaking in foreign language)",
        "start": 228.465,
        "duration": 3.078
    },
    {
        "text": "(loud, metallic banging)",
        "start": 231.543,
        "duration": 1.35
    },
    {
        "text": "(sizzling oil)",
        "start": 232.893,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "(banging and scraping metal)",
        "start": 236.253,
        "duration": 2.998
    },
    {
        "text": "(sizzling)\n(scraping)",
        "start": 239.251,
        "duration": 4.5
    },
    {
        "text": "(clanks)",
        "start": 249.824,
        "duration": 1.116
    },
    {
        "text": "(laughs)",
        "start": 250.94,
        "duration": 2.083
    },
    {
        "text": "(clanks)",
        "start": 253.023,
        "duration": 1.891
    },
    {
        "text": "(clanks)",
        "start": 254.914,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "(speaking in foreign language)",
        "start": 255.747,
        "duration": 4.012
    },
    {
        "text": "(metallic banging)",
        "start": 259.759,
        "duration": 2.404
    },
    {
        "text": "(scraping)",
        "start": 262.163,
        "duration": 1.997
    },
    {
        "text": "The more I watch her as\nshe makes the pad thai...",
        "start": 264.16,
        "duration": 2.91
    },
    {
        "text": "I don't even know if I\nwould call it stir-frying",
        "start": 267.07,
        "duration": 2.5
    },
    {
        "text": "because it's such a juicy,",
        "start": 269.57,
        "duration": 2.94
    },
    {
        "text": "such a sloshy mixture\nof sauces and noodles.",
        "start": 272.51,
        "duration": 4.63
    },
    {
        "text": "It's so wet.",
        "start": 277.14,
        "duration": 2.36
    },
    {
        "text": "It's a wet fry.",
        "start": 279.5,
        "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
        "text": "She controls the fire here\nbecause she also mentioned to me",
        "start": 280.62,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": "that she only burns wood\nso that she gets the flame",
        "start": 283.38,
        "duration": 2.79
    },
    {
        "text": "so that she can control the fire",
        "start": 286.17,
        "duration": 1.51
    },
    {
        "text": "but also because it's a batch,\nshe cooks it by the batch,",
        "start": 287.68,
        "duration": 4.25
    },
    {
        "text": "it's not like a scorching...",
        "start": 291.93,
        "duration": 1.95
    },
    {
        "text": "You get the smokiness from\nthe actual burning of the wood",
        "start": 293.88,
        "duration": 2.41
    },
    {
        "text": "but not from the heat of the wok.",
        "start": 296.29,
        "duration": 3.42
    },
    {
        "text": "But just the way she has it mastered down.",
        "start": 299.71,
        "duration": 2.303
    },
    {
        "text": "Again, she could, by all means,",
        "start": 303.508,
        "duration": 2.502
    },
    {
        "text": "make pad thai with her eyes closed.",
        "start": 306.01,
        "duration": 1.38
    },
    {
        "text": "Just the methods, the system,",
        "start": 307.39,
        "duration": 2.58
    },
    {
        "text": "the process which she has\ndeveloped and practiced",
        "start": 309.97,
        "duration": 3.86
    },
    {
        "text": "for over 45 years and mastered.",
        "start": 313.83,
        "duration": 3.39
    },
    {
        "text": "That is mastery.",
        "start": 317.22,
        "duration": 1.26
    },
    {
        "text": "But then to get her batch started,",
        "start": 318.48,
        "duration": 1.74
    },
    {
        "text": "what she does is, I believe\nshe adds in some lard,",
        "start": 320.22,
        "duration": 3.81
    },
    {
        "text": "then tosses in the noodles,",
        "start": 324.03,
        "duration": 1.41
    },
    {
        "text": "then a few scoops of a\nmixture of palm sugar syrup",
        "start": 325.44,
        "duration": 4.14
    },
    {
        "text": "as well as tamarind\nsauce and pours that in,",
        "start": 329.58,
        "duration": 3.15
    },
    {
        "text": "and it just kinda sloshes\naround the noodles in that sauce",
        "start": 332.73,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "in that caramelly syrup",
        "start": 336.33,
        "duration": 2.96
    },
    {
        "text": "thickness.",
        "start": 340.16,
        "duration": 1.2
    },
    {
        "text": "And that bubbles away,",
        "start": 341.36,
        "duration": 1.36
    },
    {
        "text": "but it's a really a matter\nof mastering the technique",
        "start": 342.72,
        "duration": 4.1
    },
    {
        "text": "and also mastering the fire and the heat",
        "start": 346.82,
        "duration": 2.68
    },
    {
        "text": "because I can guarantee that\nif you don't have experience,",
        "start": 349.5,
        "duration": 4.83
    },
    {
        "text": "if you don't know what you're doing,",
        "start": 354.33,
        "duration": 1.19
    },
    {
        "text": "you'll end up with like a\nclump, a blob of noodles",
        "start": 355.52,
        "duration": 3.16
    },
    {
        "text": "that will all stick together,",
        "start": 358.68,
        "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
        "text": "but she keeps the noodles separately.",
        "start": 360.52,
        "duration": 1.9
    },
    {
        "text": "She knows how to control the fire,",
        "start": 362.42,
        "duration": 2.87
    },
    {
        "text": "knows how to control the different sauces",
        "start": 365.29,
        "duration": 3.61
    },
    {
        "text": "to pair with the noodles.",
        "start": 368.9,
        "duration": 1.85
    },
    {
        "text": "And then she just kinda\nworks that in slowly.",
        "start": 370.75,
        "duration": 3.75
    },
    {
        "text": "She works it slowly.",
        "start": 374.5,
        "duration": 1.23
    },
    {
        "text": "And then I just love how\nshe drops in the eggs.",
        "start": 375.73,
        "duration": 2.297
    },
    {
        "text": "(taps)",
        "start": 378.027,
        "duration": 1.917
    },
    {
        "text": "(banging metal)",
        "start": 382.074,
        "duration": 2.667
    },
    {
        "text": "(speaking in foreign language)",
        "start": 386.896,
        "duration": 3.917
    },
    {
        "text": "(sizzling)\n(metallic banging)",
        "start": 391.884,
        "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
        "text": "(scraping metal)",
        "start": 397.726,
        "duration": 2.75
    },
    {
        "text": "(loud sizzling)",
        "start": 405.035,
        "duration": 2.565
    },
    {
        "text": "(woman speaking in foreign language)",
        "start": 407.6,
        "duration": 3.466
    },
    {
        "text": "(sizzling)",
        "start": 411.066,
        "duration": 2.997
    },
    {
        "text": "(banging on metal)",
        "start": 414.063,
        "duration": 2.917
    },
    {
        "text": "(speaks in foreign language)",
        "start": 419.254,
        "duration": 3.676
    },
    {
        "text": "And then right before serving,",
        "start": 422.93,
        "duration": 1.07
    },
    {
        "text": "what she does is she takes a handful",
        "start": 424.0,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
        "text": "of thua ngok, which are bean sprouts,",
        "start": 425.68,
        "duration": 2.73
    },
    {
        "text": "tosses them on top, and just\nfolds it into the noodles",
        "start": 428.41,
        "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
        "text": "just so they slightly wilt\nunder the heat of those noodles",
        "start": 430.43,
        "duration": 3.7
    },
    {
        "text": "and then puts it onto your\nplate, and that's a portion.",
        "start": 434.13,
        "duration": 1.81
    },
    {
        "text": "And I'm sure they get their\nbanana blossoms right from here",
        "start": 435.94,
        "duration": 2.46
    },
    {
        "text": "even the green mango.",
        "start": 438.4,
        "duration": 1.34
    },
    {
        "text": "Everything is right from here.",
        "start": 439.74,
        "duration": 1.523
    },
    {
        "text": "That is a big banana blossom right there",
        "start": 442.26,
        "duration": 2.345
    },
    {
        "text": "(woman speaks in foreign language)",
        "start": 444.605,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "used to garnish pad thai.",
        "start": 445.438,
        "duration": 1.694
    },
    {
        "text": "(lively, rhythmic music)",
        "start": 447.132,
        "duration": 4.174
    },
    {
        "text": "There's a little dog\nunderneath the table (laughs).",
        "start": 451.306,
        "duration": 2.904
    },
    {
        "text": "(woman speaking foreign language)",
        "start": 454.21,
        "duration": 1.38
    },
    {
        "text": "There's two different\nversions you can get, right?",
        "start": 455.59,
        "duration": 1.28
    },
    {
        "text": "Just the normal and the pi-se.",
        "start": 456.87,
        "duration": 1.8
    },
    {
        "text": "Pi-se comes with two eggs, so I got pi-se.",
        "start": 458.67,
        "duration": 2.92
    },
    {
        "text": "And I think the eggs are both kinda like",
        "start": 461.59,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": "folded within your noodles.",
        "start": 464.35,
        "duration": 1.991
    },
    {
        "text": "(rattling metal)",
        "start": 466.341,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Chopsticks eat with chopsticks (mutters).",
        "start": 467.174,
        "duration": 1.386
    },
    {
        "text": "I love these high benches with the tables,",
        "start": 468.56,
        "duration": 3.57
    },
    {
        "text": "but quickly, before I start eating,",
        "start": 472.13,
        "duration": 1.94
    },
    {
        "text": "before I taste test...",
        "start": 474.07,
        "duration": 2.05
    },
    {
        "text": "Or should I taste test\nfirst before I tell you?",
        "start": 476.12,
        "duration": 2.23
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah, maybe I should\ntaste this right now first",
        "start": 478.35,
        "duration": 1.89
    },
    {
        "text": "while it's hot and fresh.",
        "start": 480.24,
        "duration": 1.42
    },
    {
        "text": "But I just wanted to tell you\na little bit about pad thai,",
        "start": 481.66,
        "duration": 2.82
    },
    {
        "text": "about the history of pad thai.",
        "start": 484.48,
        "duration": 1.92
    },
    {
        "text": "And also, pad thai is not...",
        "start": 486.4,
        "duration": 1.41
    },
    {
        "text": "It's not a dish that I\nactually eat very often.",
        "start": 487.81,
        "duration": 3.14
    },
    {
        "text": "It is one of the most\nwell-known Thai dishes,",
        "start": 490.95,
        "duration": 1.86
    },
    {
        "text": "and it is popular in Thailand as well.",
        "start": 492.81,
        "duration": 2.43
    },
    {
        "text": "But just because there's\nso many other dishes,",
        "start": 495.24,
        "duration": 1.71
    },
    {
        "text": "and pad thai tends to be kinda\nlike on the sweeter side,",
        "start": 496.95,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "it's not usually my personal favorite,",
        "start": 499.35,
        "duration": 2.58
    },
    {
        "text": "but I am very excited\nto try this pad thai,",
        "start": 501.93,
        "duration": 2.2
    },
    {
        "text": "one, because she's such a legend.",
        "start": 504.13,
        "duration": 1.953
    },
    {
        "text": "She makes only one dish,",
        "start": 507.504,
        "duration": 1.236
    },
    {
        "text": "and she has perfected it.",
        "start": 508.74,
        "duration": 2.44
    },
    {
        "text": "And no matter what, I respect\nthat, and I love that.",
        "start": 511.18,
        "duration": 4.27
    },
    {
        "text": "So it is a true honor to be\nhere, to taste her plate.",
        "start": 515.45,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "Once she dishes out your plate\nof pad thai from the wok,",
        "start": 518.57,
        "duration": 2.74
    },
    {
        "text": "then they sprinkle on a\nspoonful of crushed peanuts",
        "start": 521.31,
        "duration": 2.91
    },
    {
        "text": "and then a few...",
        "start": 524.22,
        "duration": 1.26
    },
    {
        "text": "Sometimes, it's chives,",
        "start": 526.46,
        "duration": 1.41
    },
    {
        "text": "but she's using green onions.",
        "start": 527.87,
        "duration": 1.697
    },
    {
        "text": "(background conversations\nin foreign language)",
        "start": 529.567,
        "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Mm.",
        "start": 534.719,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh, wow.",
        "start": 537.71,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "(smacks)",
        "start": 539.847,
        "duration": 2.443
    },
    {
        "text": "The texture of the noodles is amazing.",
        "start": 542.29,
        "duration": 2.84
    },
    {
        "text": "It's so...",
        "start": 545.13,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "They're elastic-y.",
        "start": 548.211,
        "duration": 1.599
    },
    {
        "text": "You could probably tie\nsomething up with them,",
        "start": 549.81,
        "duration": 1.62
    },
    {
        "text": "but at the same time",
        "start": 551.43,
        "duration": 1.138
    },
    {
        "text": "(dog yelps loudly)",
        "start": 552.568,
        "duration": 1.052
    },
    {
        "text": "Whoa.",
        "start": 553.62,
        "duration": 1.068
    },
    {
        "text": "(people speaking in foreign language)",
        "start": 554.688,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "There's the little dog (mutters).",
        "start": 555.521,
        "duration": 1.362
    },
    {
        "text": "(speaks in foreign language)",
        "start": 558.621,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "At the same time, they've\nabsorbed just the right amount of",
        "start": 559.454,
        "duration": 3.576
    },
    {
        "text": "that makham, that palm\nsugar, the tamarind,",
        "start": 563.03,
        "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
        "text": "the sauces, the oil.",
        "start": 567.11,
        "duration": 2.29
    },
    {
        "text": "You do taste sweet at first.",
        "start": 569.4,
        "duration": 1.55
    },
    {
        "text": "Pad thai is always on the sweeter side,",
        "start": 570.95,
        "duration": 2.433
    },
    {
        "text": "but then, at the same time,\nthe sweetness kinda mellows out",
        "start": 574.47,
        "duration": 3.78
    },
    {
        "text": "because it's palm sugar.",
        "start": 578.25,
        "duration": 0.9
    },
    {
        "text": "It's not that sharp sugar, processed",
        "start": 579.15,
        "duration": 4.71
    },
    {
        "text": "sugar, like very sharp sweetness.",
        "start": 583.86,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "It's more of a mellow sweetness,",
        "start": 585.86,
        "duration": 1.64
    },
    {
        "text": "and the richness of those\nyolks, those duck yolk eggs.",
        "start": 587.5,
        "duration": 3.73
    },
    {
        "text": "You can see that the sauce is so thick.",
        "start": 591.23,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "It just coats onto your chopsticks.",
        "start": 592.99,
        "duration": 1.88
    },
    {
        "text": "It's so thick and sticky.",
        "start": 594.87,
        "duration": 2.413
    },
    {
        "text": "(child speaking foreign language)",
        "start": 597.283,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "With my chopstick (mutters).",
        "start": 598.116,
        "duration": 1.964
    },
    {
        "text": "But really quickly, just to tell you",
        "start": 600.08,
        "duration": 1.35
    },
    {
        "text": "a little about the history of pad thai,",
        "start": 601.43,
        "duration": 2.34
    },
    {
        "text": "pad thai is not an ancient dish.",
        "start": 603.77,
        "duration": 1.723
    },
    {
        "text": "It previously was not even a\ntraditional dish of Thailand.",
        "start": 607.29,
        "duration": 3.69
    },
    {
        "text": "But it only dates back to the 1930s",
        "start": 610.98,
        "duration": 2.18
    },
    {
        "text": "when the prime minister at that time...",
        "start": 613.16,
        "duration": 2.3
    },
    {
        "text": "He was developing Thailand.",
        "start": 615.46,
        "duration": 1.87
    },
    {
        "text": "He's the one who's responsible for even",
        "start": 617.33,
        "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
        "text": "changing the name to Thailand,",
        "start": 619.35,
        "duration": 1.92
    },
    {
        "text": "Thailand to Thailand.",
        "start": 621.27,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "Back in the 1930s, the prime minister,",
        "start": 623.37,
        "duration": 2.67
    },
    {
        "text": "his house help made a\nnoodle dish, kway teow.",
        "start": 626.04,
        "duration": 2.9
    },
    {
        "text": "And kway teow is originally",
        "start": 628.94,
        "duration": 1.93
    },
    {
        "text": "rice noodles originally from China,",
        "start": 630.87,
        "duration": 2.95
    },
    {
        "text": "which were adapted into Thailand.",
        "start": 633.82,
        "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
        "text": "But his house helper would\nmake a type of kway teow",
        "start": 635.42,
        "duration": 3.91
    },
    {
        "text": "that maybe was her own style.",
        "start": 639.33,
        "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
        "text": "She would fry the noodles,",
        "start": 641.93,
        "duration": 1.4
    },
    {
        "text": "and the prime minister loved",
        "start": 643.33,
        "duration": 1.87
    },
    {
        "text": "the noodles so much that he said,",
        "start": 645.2,
        "duration": 2.047
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Let's make this into a dish that unifies,",
        "start": 647.247,
        "duration": 4.93
    },
    {
        "text": "\"that brings the people\nof Thailand together.\"",
        "start": 652.177,
        "duration": 3.363
    },
    {
        "text": "And that's why it's called pad thai.",
        "start": 655.54,
        "duration": 2.19
    },
    {
        "text": "That's why it's called stir-fried thai.",
        "start": 657.73,
        "duration": 2.393
    },
    {
        "text": "And so that's when pad thai was created",
        "start": 660.98,
        "duration": 4.12
    },
    {
        "text": "originally with Chinese roots,",
        "start": 665.1,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
        "text": "but then he added many\ndifferent Thai ingredients:",
        "start": 666.78,
        "duration": 2.73
    },
    {
        "text": "protein sources, the eggs,",
        "start": 669.51,
        "duration": 2.98
    },
    {
        "text": "the Thai ingredients like palm\nsugar, like sour tamarind,",
        "start": 672.49,
        "duration": 4.873
    },
    {
        "text": "and then balanced the\nflavor so that it was sweet,",
        "start": 678.2,
        "duration": 2.7
    },
    {
        "text": "so that it was sour, a little bit spicy,",
        "start": 680.9,
        "duration": 3.31
    },
    {
        "text": "some of the herbs and\nsome of the ingredients",
        "start": 684.21,
        "duration": 2.87
    },
    {
        "text": "that you can find right\nin Central Thailand.",
        "start": 687.08,
        "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
        "text": "Additionally, Ba Lek was\nalso mentioning that,",
        "start": 689.72,
        "duration": 3.86
    },
    {
        "text": "originally, a traditional\nversion or an old version",
        "start": 693.58,
        "duration": 2.96
    },
    {
        "text": "of pad thai was to be served with",
        "start": 696.54,
        "duration": 2.36
    },
    {
        "text": "ma-fuang, which is starfruit,",
        "start": 698.9,
        "duration": 2.94
    },
    {
        "text": "but then, after that,\nwhen it wasn't the season",
        "start": 701.84,
        "duration": 3.15
    },
    {
        "text": "or when there's no starfruit available,",
        "start": 704.99,
        "duration": 2.03
    },
    {
        "text": "people started using green mango.",
        "start": 707.02,
        "duration": 1.95
    },
    {
        "text": "So she still serves\ngreen mango on the table",
        "start": 708.97,
        "duration": 1.85
    },
    {
        "text": "to eat with your pad thai,",
        "start": 710.82,
        "duration": 1.2
    },
    {
        "text": "and now even one step further,",
        "start": 712.02,
        "duration": 1.29
    },
    {
        "text": "most of the time in Bangkok,",
        "start": 713.31,
        "duration": 1.01
    },
    {
        "text": "you don't even find it\nserved with green mango.",
        "start": 714.32,
        "duration": 1.46
    },
    {
        "text": "It's rare.",
        "start": 715.78,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "I don't know if I've ever seen\nit served with green mango,",
        "start": 716.613,
        "duration": 2.297
    },
    {
        "text": "but it's served with just lime slices",
        "start": 718.91,
        "duration": 2.43
    },
    {
        "text": "to squeeze on lime because it's faster.",
        "start": 721.34,
        "duration": 1.46
    },
    {
        "text": "It's easier.",
        "start": 722.8,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "It's more sour.",
        "start": 723.633,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "It's less expensive.",
        "start": 724.466,
        "duration": 2.134
    },
    {
        "text": "The green mango, that is awesome.",
        "start": 726.6,
        "duration": 1.7
    },
    {
        "text": "And then, because I love sourness",
        "start": 728.3,
        "duration": 1.43
    },
    {
        "text": "and also to balance that\nsweetness, I'll squeeze on lime.",
        "start": 729.73,
        "duration": 3.343
    },
    {
        "text": "In addition to the fresh accompaniments,",
        "start": 736.69,
        "duration": 1.43
    },
    {
        "text": "we've also got some of the seasonings.",
        "start": 738.12,
        "duration": 1.33
    },
    {
        "text": "There's fish sauce.",
        "start": 739.45,
        "duration": 1.04
    },
    {
        "text": "There is extra sugar that you can put on.",
        "start": 740.49,
        "duration": 2.61
    },
    {
        "text": "It's already very sweet, in my opinion,",
        "start": 743.1,
        "duration": 2.01
    },
    {
        "text": "but some people even add extra sugar.",
        "start": 745.11,
        "duration": 2.07
    },
    {
        "text": "And then the main thing that I want:",
        "start": 747.18,
        "duration": 1.575
    },
    {
        "text": "(loudly opens container)",
        "start": 748.755,
        "duration": 4.155
    },
    {
        "text": "Sprinkle on a little bit of chili flakes.",
        "start": 752.91,
        "duration": 2.253
    },
    {
        "text": "Bump up the heat,",
        "start": 756.6,
        "duration": 0.863
    },
    {
        "text": "and then just kinda stir this around.",
        "start": 758.3,
        "duration": 1.24
    },
    {
        "text": "I wanna get some of that green\nmango for sure in this bite.",
        "start": 759.54,
        "duration": 3.08
    },
    {
        "text": "And then there's lime juice on here.",
        "start": 762.62,
        "duration": 1.7
    },
    {
        "text": "There's chili to balance the flavor.",
        "start": 764.32,
        "duration": 1.86
    },
    {
        "text": "And another reason why noodles,",
        "start": 766.18,
        "duration": 1.64
    },
    {
        "text": "especially soup noodles but\nalso pad thai, other noodles,",
        "start": 767.82,
        "duration": 2.44
    },
    {
        "text": "are so popular in Thailand",
        "start": 770.26,
        "duration": 2.93
    },
    {
        "text": "is because they're so customizable.",
        "start": 773.19,
        "duration": 1.75
    },
    {
        "text": "I mean, that's the reason they give you",
        "start": 775.89,
        "duration": 2.06
    },
    {
        "text": "the different seasonings.",
        "start": 777.95,
        "duration": 1.04
    },
    {
        "text": "If it's not salty enough for\nyou, you can add fish sauce.",
        "start": 778.99,
        "duration": 2.19
    },
    {
        "text": "If it's not sweet enough\nfor you, you can add sugar.",
        "start": 781.18,
        "duration": 1.78
    },
    {
        "text": "If it's not spicy enough for you,",
        "start": 782.96,
        "duration": 2.28
    },
    {
        "text": "nobody minds if you add a lot of chili.",
        "start": 785.24,
        "duration": 2.623
    },
    {
        "text": "(loud, airy music)",
        "start": 787.863,
        "duration": 2.917
    },
    {
        "text": "Mm.",
        "start": 794.398,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "(loud bang in background)",
        "start": 796.618,
        "duration": 1.2
    },
    {
        "text": "With the green mango, it's amazing",
        "start": 797.818,
        "duration": 2.232
    },
    {
        "text": "because the noodles are so sweet,",
        "start": 800.05,
        "duration": 3.22
    },
    {
        "text": "but then, with that\nburst of sour green mango",
        "start": 803.27,
        "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
        "text": "and that crunch...",
        "start": 808.68,
        "duration": 2.13
    },
    {
        "text": "Mm.",
        "start": 810.81,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "That just fully complements\nthe sweetness for me.",
        "start": 812.579,
        "duration": 3.001
    },
    {
        "text": "Then with that spicy dried\nchili smokiness at the end.",
        "start": 815.58,
        "duration": 4.34
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm gonna squeeze this\nwith a little more lime",
        "start": 819.92,
        "duration": 3.07
    },
    {
        "text": "just to give it",
        "start": 822.99,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "a sharpness of lime.",
        "start": 826.214,
        "duration": 1.583
    },
    {
        "text": "(airy music)",
        "start": 827.797,
        "duration": 2.417
    },
    {
        "text": "And I'll take a time-out to\nchase with a banana blossom.",
        "start": 831.96,
        "duration": 2.61
    },
    {
        "text": "In Thai, it's called huapli.",
        "start": 834.57,
        "duration": 1.31
    },
    {
        "text": "It's also almost mandatory\nto serve with pad thai.",
        "start": 835.88,
        "duration": 2.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Normally, it's actually\ncooked in different dishes,",
        "start": 839.44,
        "duration": 1.92
    },
    {
        "text": "but this is one of the only\ndishes where you eat it raw.",
        "start": 841.36,
        "duration": 2.55
    },
    {
        "text": "And it's always available with pad thai.",
        "start": 843.91,
        "duration": 2.67
    },
    {
        "text": "(smacks)",
        "start": 848.306,
        "duration": 0.894
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah.",
        "start": 849.2,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "It's chalky, doesn't actually\nhave a lot of flavor,",
        "start": 850.033,
        "duration": 3.657
    },
    {
        "text": "almost like a side of milkiness",
        "start": 853.69,
        "duration": 1.86
    },
    {
        "text": "and a little bit of sweetness,",
        "start": 855.55,
        "duration": 0.89
    },
    {
        "text": "but it is kinda like chalky.",
        "start": 856.44,
        "duration": 1.99
    },
    {
        "text": "It's kinda dry, I think.",
        "start": 858.43,
        "duration": 2.35
    },
    {
        "text": "But for me, the benefit\nis when you're taking",
        "start": 860.78,
        "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
        "text": "a bite of pad thai and it's kinda sweet,",
        "start": 863.34,
        "duration": 2.27
    },
    {
        "text": "the banana blossom just kinda\nlike completely cleanses,",
        "start": 865.61,
        "duration": 3.853
    },
    {
        "text": "and then that rejuvenates your taste buds",
        "start": 870.95,
        "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
        "text": "and then you can take\nanother bite of pad thai.",
        "start": 872.97,
        "duration": 2.435
    },
    {
        "text": "(slow, airy music)",
        "start": 875.405,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "And you're like",
        "start": 878.285,
        "duration": 1.25
    },
    {
        "text": "really feel the flavors of the pad thai",
        "start": 881.25,
        "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
        "text": "even more",
        "start": 882.85,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "exuberantly",
        "start": 884.85,
        "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
        "text": "after taking a bite",
        "start": 886.35,
        "duration": 1.27
    },
    {
        "text": "of the banana blossom",
        "start": 887.62,
        "duration": 1.195
    },
    {
        "text": "(loud, rhythmic music)",
        "start": 888.815,
        "duration": 2.915
    },
    {
        "text": "She's gonna make a new batch.",
        "start": 891.73,
        "duration": 1.996
    },
    {
        "text": "(loud, rhythmic music)",
        "start": 893.726,
        "duration": 3.25
    },
    {
        "text": "Mm.",
        "start": 897.987,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "I could eat every bite\nwith an entire 50/50 ratio",
        "start": 902.17,
        "duration": 4.39
    },
    {
        "text": "of green mango to the noodles.",
        "start": 906.56,
        "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
        "text": "Mm.",
        "start": 909.12,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "I think the green mango\nis what makes it for me.",
        "start": 911.573,
        "duration": 1.902
    },
    {
        "text": "(airy piano music)",
        "start": 913.475,
        "duration": 2.917
    },
    {
        "text": "(loud, rhythmic music)",
        "start": 921.983,
        "duration": 2.571
    },
    {
        "text": "And I'm getting down to my last\nfew bites of my first plate,",
        "start": 924.554,
        "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
        "text": "but as I keep on eating it,",
        "start": 930.07,
        "duration": 3.23
    },
    {
        "text": "you can really taste the richness of it,",
        "start": 933.3,
        "duration": 2.61
    },
    {
        "text": "the amount of lard in\nhere, the duck egg yolks.",
        "start": 935.91,
        "duration": 2.44
    },
    {
        "text": "It is rich.",
        "start": 938.35,
        "duration": 1.47
    },
    {
        "text": "It's hardy.",
        "start": 939.82,
        "duration": 0.883
    },
    {
        "text": "It's warming.",
        "start": 943.23,
        "duration": 0.987
    },
    {
        "text": "(loud, airy music)",
        "start": 944.217,
        "duration": 2.917
    },
    {
        "text": "(taps)",
        "start": 949.449,
        "duration": 0.896
    },
    {
        "text": "(loud, airy music)",
        "start": 950.345,
        "duration": 2.917
    },
    {
        "text": "I haven't even had any water yet,",
        "start": 954.45,
        "duration": 1.29
    },
    {
        "text": "but they also use the\nreally old-style Thai cups.",
        "start": 955.74,
        "duration": 2.24
    },
    {
        "text": "I think they're made from aluminum,",
        "start": 957.98,
        "duration": 1.49
    },
    {
        "text": "and it's all self service at the front.",
        "start": 959.47,
        "duration": 1.58
    },
    {
        "text": "You can serve yourself water.",
        "start": 961.05,
        "duration": 1.45
    },
    {
        "text": "I love these cups, too.",
        "start": 965.38,
        "duration": 1.556
    },
    {
        "text": "(reverberating piano music)",
        "start": 966.936,
        "duration": 3.667
    },
    {
        "text": "(woman laughs)",
        "start": 973.039,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "As I continue to eat it, you\ncould get the richness of it,",
        "start": 973.872,
        "duration": 2.568
    },
    {
        "text": "that lard, the eggs, the yolks.",
        "start": 976.44,
        "duration": 3.27
    },
    {
        "text": "It was very good for a plate of pad thai.",
        "start": 979.71,
        "duration": 2.53
    },
    {
        "text": "And just the history in that dish",
        "start": 982.24,
        "duration": 2.33
    },
    {
        "text": "and the history in Ba Lek herself",
        "start": 984.57,
        "duration": 2.57
    },
    {
        "text": "and how long she's been making it,",
        "start": 987.14,
        "duration": 1.86
    },
    {
        "text": "how she's mastered pad thai.",
        "start": 989.0,
        "duration": 2.14
    },
    {
        "text": "But again, pad thai just in\ngeneral is not my favorite dish.",
        "start": 991.14,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "It is a little too sweet\nfor me to eat regularly.",
        "start": 993.86,
        "duration": 3.23
    },
    {
        "text": "But that being said,\nI did really enjoy it.",
        "start": 997.09,
        "duration": 1.75
    },
    {
        "text": "I enjoyed this entire experience,",
        "start": 998.84,
        "duration": 1.66
    },
    {
        "text": "and just getting to taste her pad thai",
        "start": 1000.5,
        "duration": 2.2
    },
    {
        "text": "that she's been making so long,",
        "start": 1002.7,
        "duration": 1.27
    },
    {
        "text": "that she's been perfecting for so long.",
        "start": 1003.97,
        "duration": 2.51
    },
    {
        "text": "She is a legend of pad thai.",
        "start": 1006.48,
        "duration": 2.55
    },
    {
        "text": "And my utmost respect to her there.",
        "start": 1009.03,
        "duration": 3.24
    },
    {
        "text": "She's so nice as well.",
        "start": 1012.27,
        "duration": 1.34
    },
    {
        "text": "She's so welcoming.",
        "start": 1013.61,
        "duration": 1.36
    },
    {
        "text": "And it's still completely family-run.",
        "start": 1014.97,
        "duration": 1.46
    },
    {
        "text": "It's her daughters that also help.",
        "start": 1016.43,
        "duration": 1.47
    },
    {
        "text": "And so that was an honor to\nhave this chance to drive here,",
        "start": 1017.9,
        "duration": 4.78
    },
    {
        "text": "to come here, to spend time, hanging out,",
        "start": 1022.68,
        "duration": 1.98
    },
    {
        "text": "to watch her as she\nmethodically, expertly,",
        "start": 1024.66,
        "duration": 4.43
    },
    {
        "text": "again, mastering-ly\nprepared that pad thai.",
        "start": 1029.09,
        "duration": 3.407
    },
    {
        "text": "And then, yeah, that was just a lot of fun",
        "start": 1032.497,
        "duration": 1.943
    },
    {
        "text": "and a learning experience for me.",
        "start": 1034.44,
        "duration": 1.72
    },
    {
        "text": "So that's it for this video.",
        "start": 1036.16,
        "duration": 1.04
    },
    {
        "text": "I'll have all the information\nin the description box below",
        "start": 1037.2,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "so you can check out.",
        "start": 1039.3,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "I'll have directions on\nhow to get here as well.",
        "start": 1040.133,
        "duration": 2.567
    },
    {
        "text": "And I wanna say a big thank\nyou for watching this video.",
        "start": 1042.7,
        "duration": 1.89
    },
    {
        "text": "Please remember to give it a\nthumbs up if you enjoyed it.",
        "start": 1044.59,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "Leave a comment below.",
        "start": 1046.35,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "I'd love to hear from you.",
        "start": 1047.183,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "And if you're not already subscribed,",
        "start": 1048.016,
        "duration": 1.824
    },
    {
        "text": "click Subscribe and also\nclick the little bell icon.",
        "start": 1049.84,
        "duration": 2.61
    },
    {
        "text": "Click that bell icon so\nthat you'll get notified",
